810
00:46:05,960 --> 00:46:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] U tome ti govori, znači sve je moj dostupno, ima low.

811
00:46:08,960 --> 00:46:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, to je svakako.

812
00:46:10,960 --> 00:46:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

813
00:46:11,960 --> 00:46:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ja dođem na svadu, postratim ko tebe.

814
00:46:13,960 --> 00:46:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, evo ugodno, ugodno s koristim.

815
00:46:15,960 --> 00:46:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

816
00:46:16,960 --> 00:46:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo idemo mi polako prema kraju, ali to smo čak komentirali.

817
00:46:20,960 --> 00:46:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hoće mi Hajduk ili da, hoće mi prvo.

818
00:46:22,960 --> 00:46:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijem ja te reći.

819
00:46:23,960 --> 00:46:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

820
00:46:24,960 --> 00:46:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijem da radim prokledstva.

821
00:46:26,960 --> 00:46:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pozor, kako prokledstvo, ti si izdelno.

822
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] Uklavno sam Hajduk.

823
00:46:30,960 --> 00:46:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nadajući se tako, da navijanje za Hajduk i postoje na noštama.

824
00:46:33,960 --> 00:46:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja kažem da će biti Dinamo 5.

825
00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Poznajem moga prijatelja Mačuća.

826
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš ti Mačuća, i Mačuća?

827
00:46:38,960 --> 00:46:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mačuća.

828
00:46:39,960 --> 00:46:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] Maču, moj prijatelji, on je najveći Hajduk vas na svijetu.

829
00:46:42,960 --> 00:46:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, poznajem moga prijatelja dragova i ja kažem da će biti to.

830
00:46:45,960 --> 00:46:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Poznajš vas ja.

831
00:46:46,960 --> 00:46:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, bit će pet vodova prednaci za Dinamo, bit će Dinamo prvak.

832
00:46:51,960 --> 00:46:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] i ko izgubi vodi na Božja kod bule na ruč.

833
00:46:54,960 --> 00:46:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] Može, može.

834
00:46:55,960 --> 00:46:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj, jesmo kako?

835
00:46:57,960 --> 00:47:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, da govorim, a ako nisu vidjeli, čuli smo.

836
00:47:01,960 --> 00:47:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Čuli smo.

837
00:47:02,960 --> 00:47:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da ponovimo pravila.

838
00:47:03,960 --> 00:47:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem Dinamo prvak, ti kažeš Hajduk.

839
00:47:05,960 --> 00:47:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne kažem Hajduk, ali...

840
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tipiči domvradski stav, ovo su domvradski.

841
00:47:10,960 --> 00:47:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ti će.

842
00:47:12,960 --> 00:47:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ko izgubi vodi kod bule?

843
00:47:14,960 --> 00:47:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je ogovor.

844
00:47:16,960 --> 00:47:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je ogovor.

845
00:47:17,960 --> 00:47:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da ne bude turčan.

846
00:47:18,960 --> 00:47:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne žbi turčan.

847
00:47:21,960 --> 00:47:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kulturi smo pristojni.

848
00:47:22,960 --> 00:47:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mi, nego jači.

849
00:47:24,960 --> 00:47:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je zadnje pitanje bilo koje sam nadopisao kemijskom.

850
00:47:28,960 --> 00:47:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Senad Aldića, smo spominjali.

851
00:47:31,960 --> 00:47:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ima je ovaj njegov prezivljenjaka.

852
00:47:32,960 --> 00:47:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Aldić kojim je nedavno zabranjen u ulaz u Hrvatsku.

853
00:47:36,960 --> 00:47:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže to, meni je zabranjen u ulaz u Hrvatsku.

854
00:47:38,960 --> 00:47:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] A mi, Andreju i Arka, tako velikodušno puštamo u BiH, iako on...

855
00:47:43,960 --> 00:47:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] Otvor nam za ovaj treći titi.

856
00:47:45,960 --> 00:47:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] Parafrazirat ću ga tako da...

857
00:47:47,960 --> 00:47:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] I rušim ustani poradak.

858
00:47:48,960 --> 00:47:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] I rušim ustani poradak.

859
00:47:49,960 --> 00:47:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Spomenuo Ivanu Petrović i mene.

860
00:47:51,960 --> 00:47:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam doista zašto.

861
00:47:52,960 --> 00:47:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] U kom dijelu ja rušim ustani poradak.

862
00:47:54,960 --> 00:47:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam u Bosni i Hercegovini bio 300 puta.

863
00:47:57,960 --> 00:48:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] I izvještao o najgodnim stvarima.

864
00:48:00,960 --> 00:48:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] spomenuo sam i Srebrenicu.

865
00:48:02,960 --> 00:48:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] I tako da ne znam iz čega izvuku to zašto.

866
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Apsolutno se zalažem za to da Hrvatski narod u Bosni i Hercegovini

867
00:48:09,960 --> 00:48:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] bude konstitutivan, ravnopravan, da ga niko ne naglasava

868
00:48:13,960 --> 00:48:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] i da mu niko ne vira njegove predstavnike.

869
00:48:15,960 --> 00:48:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, sad ću cititati...

870
00:48:17,960 --> 00:48:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] U stvari, zvučuću kao predsjednik Zoran Milanović.

871
00:48:20,960 --> 00:48:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] Reći da nitko ne može ponižavati narod.

872
00:48:23,960 --> 00:48:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam da li ja s time rušim bilo šta

873
00:48:25,960 --> 00:48:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] ili da li pozivam na rušenje ustano poradka.

874
00:48:29,960 --> 00:48:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam od kuda izvuku Zagćak.

875
00:48:31,960 --> 00:48:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] Normalno njegove pravo.

876
00:48:32,960 --> 00:48:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sam mi rekao u nastavku te izjave

877
00:48:34,960 --> 00:48:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] da je to moj stav.

878
00:48:36,960 --> 00:48:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] I to je moj stav.

879
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je moj stav.

880
00:48:39,960 --> 00:48:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pošto je država Bosni i Hercegovina

881
00:48:41,960 --> 00:48:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] nikad jedan zarez nisam rekao

882
00:48:42,960 --> 00:48:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] protiv nje i njeznog poredka.

883
00:48:44,960 --> 00:48:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da su Hrvati, ja kao Hrvat,

884
00:48:46,960 --> 00:48:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da su Hrvati ovdje 500, 600 ili više godina.

885
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ostale moji predsjed su porijekom iz popovog polja.

886
00:48:53,960 --> 00:48:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo svoji na svome,

887
00:48:54,960 --> 00:48:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] uz dužno proštovanje prema svima.

888
00:48:56,960 --> 00:48:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je jako čudno

889
00:48:58,960 --> 00:49:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] da u 21. stoljeći

890
00:49:00,960 --> 00:49:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] većevski narod može razglasati.

891
00:49:02,960 --> 00:49:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da to nije korektno prema ljudima.

892
00:49:06,960 --> 00:49:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] I to je to.

893
00:49:07,960 --> 00:49:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ne znam ovaj.

894
00:49:09,960 --> 00:49:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam stavno na koji način sam.

895
00:49:11,960 --> 00:49:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja zato nikad nisam imao nikad problem u Bosni i Hercegovini.

896
00:49:15,960 --> 00:49:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] na kraljici ni u parlamentu ni iz presuda.

897
00:49:18,960 --> 00:49:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da pači.

898
00:49:19,960 --> 00:49:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] Čem sam bio poziv, ena burek i jogurt.

899
00:49:21,960 --> 00:49:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] Moram pastiti.

900
00:49:23,960 --> 00:49:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] Lijepe mi se kila tako da...

901
00:49:25,960 --> 00:49:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Moje iskustva s Bosnom i Hercegovini su doista preklasne.

902
00:49:28,960 --> 00:49:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tu znam ko svoj ne svojno.

903
00:49:30,960 --> 00:49:33,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad me niko krivo pogledao nije.

904
00:49:33,960 --> 00:49:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da sam ja nešto podrivo ili rušio sigurno da mi neko je rekao šta ti pričaš i šta goriš.

905
00:49:38,960 --> 00:49:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] tako da.

906
00:49:39,960 --> 00:49:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] I u osnovu ja sam isključio i opratio Srnu kroniku.

907
00:49:42,960 --> 00:49:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vrlo malo se dodicao nekoje politike.

908
00:49:46,960 --> 00:49:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

909
00:49:47,960 --> 00:49:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim ne prava da sam samo pitao svim.

910
00:49:49,960 --> 00:49:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

911
00:49:50,960 --> 00:49:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

912
00:49:51,960 --> 00:49:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

913
00:49:52,960 --> 00:49:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

914
00:49:53,960 --> 00:49:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da.

915
00:49:55,960 --> 00:49:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] U gleda.

916
00:49:57,960 --> 00:49:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek ima pravo reći što misli.

917
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nema ljutnje.

918
00:50:00,960 --> 00:50:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

919
00:50:01,960 --> 00:50:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

920
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prije kraja pala mi još jedna stvarapavet.

921
00:50:05,960 --> 00:50:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ima li, ima li na tržištu prostora, evo true crime imao dosije jarak.

922
00:50:10,960 --> 00:50:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ima li zna ovaj murder misteri.

923
00:50:12,960 --> 00:50:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] Reć smo imao misteri ove djevojke Lane Biedić.

924
00:50:15,960 --> 00:50:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znaš, ne znam se svećaš li se toga.

925
00:50:17,960 --> 00:50:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ne?

926
00:50:18,960 --> 00:50:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] To nije pravomoć, ali to je misterija koja evo meni do danas...

927
00:50:20,960 --> 00:50:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa imaš evo malu danku.

928
00:50:21,960 --> 00:50:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da danas me fascinira.

929
00:50:22,960 --> 00:50:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Malo danku u Srbiji, ali gledaj.

930
00:50:24,960 --> 00:50:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, hvala ti na pitanju.

931
00:50:26,960 --> 00:50:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Evo me kovili bereš.

932
00:50:27,960 --> 00:50:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam to pitanju.

933
00:50:28,960 --> 00:50:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] Onaj.

934
00:50:29,960 --> 00:50:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sad zanisi kako je to trik.

935
00:50:32,960 --> 00:50:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ti sad radiš tu priču.

936
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] Šadiš, šadiš, šadiš.

937
00:50:36,960 --> 00:50:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ideš imitirati emisiju i otkrije se da je malo tu.

938
00:50:38,960 --> 00:50:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, neke okolostice promijene, da.

939
00:50:40,960 --> 00:50:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] I sad to je...

940
00:50:41,960 --> 00:50:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sad zamisli da si godinu dana proslao vjetar.

941
00:50:43,960 --> 00:50:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ima još gore od toga.

942
00:50:45,960 --> 00:50:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pućaš godinu dana.

943
00:50:46,960 --> 00:50:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali si možda uvrijedio nekog.

944
00:50:48,960 --> 00:50:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] Možda si prozvao tetku, babu, Zalu, vjetaru, mamu, tatu.

945
00:50:52,960 --> 00:50:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sad zamisli da si rekao malo su to ili malo i to.

946
00:50:55,960 --> 00:50:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si gotov čovjek.

947
00:50:57,960 --> 00:50:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Razumi?

948
00:50:58,960 --> 00:50:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je...

949
00:50:59,960 --> 00:51:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Zato jedno što možeš raditi su pravomoćni slučaje.

950
00:51:01,960 --> 00:51:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ne možeš, ti ne možeš jednostavno...

951
00:51:04,960 --> 00:51:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možeš raditi nešto čili bu, čili ba.

952
00:51:08,960 --> 00:51:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nemoš.

953
00:51:09,960 --> 00:51:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako se događa...

954
00:51:11,960 --> 00:51:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] Umeđu vremenu se dogodi nešto da se kontra toga ti si gotov...

955
00:51:14,960 --> 00:51:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] Gotov si izgubio sve.

956
00:51:16,960 --> 00:51:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ozbiljna novina je da.

957
00:51:18,960 --> 00:51:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne, ne možeš izgubiti.

958
00:51:19,960 --> 00:51:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš ti sad nagađati, ali ne možeš to raditi.

959
00:51:23,960 --> 00:51:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] Andreja, pa hvala puno.

960
00:51:25,960 --> 00:51:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala tebi, bilo mi baš ugodno.

961
00:51:27,960 --> 00:51:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Super i...

962
00:51:28,960 --> 00:51:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo isli neke sad standardne vredosti jednom, nego onako...

963
00:51:31,960 --> 00:51:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Normalno.

964
00:51:32,960 --> 00:51:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mi se činulo zanimljivo.

965
00:51:33,960 --> 00:51:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Otvoreno i to je to.

966
00:51:34,960 --> 00:51:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, evo, drago mi da sam vas upoznao i tebe i kolege.

967
00:51:37,960 --> 00:51:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, želim, uvijek podržavam druge medije.

968
00:51:42,960 --> 00:51:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] I želim vam da obstanete i uspijete i da budete uticajni i da radite svoj posao na najbolji mogući način.

969
00:51:48,960 --> 00:51:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da nije lako, nikam je danas lako, ali evo, uživo sam, mislim, ugodno mi je.

970
00:51:53,960 --> 00:51:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nije mi bilo, ovaj, nijednom trenutku neugodno.

971
00:51:58,960 --> 00:52:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje namoći uporo?

972
00:52:00,960 --> 00:52:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ti nisvi ću...

973
00:52:01,960 --> 00:52:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde, evo sad ću reći.

974
00:52:03,960 --> 00:52:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Navukuo smo dakarne.

975
00:52:04,960 --> 00:52:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde, ću biti prvak, možda ću progutat te svoje riječi u svim lju.

976
00:52:08,960 --> 00:52:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali živi bilo pa vidjelo.

977
00:52:10,960 --> 00:52:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo se na Božjaku.

978
00:52:11,960 --> 00:52:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde.

979
00:52:12,960 --> 00:52:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] U svakvam slučaju.

980
00:52:13,960 --> 00:52:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala, pozdrav.

981
00:52:14,960 --> 00:52:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Gledateljica i gledateljima, bio to.

982
00:52:16,960 --> 00:52:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Andrija Jarak, nadam se da ste uživali isto koliko je i nazvojica u ovom podcastu.

983
00:52:20,960 --> 00:52:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] A mi se vidimo uskoro u sljedećoj epizodi.

